with mock.patch.object(PyQt5.QtWidgets.QMessageBox, 'question',
    return_value=PyQt5.QtWidgets.QMessageBox.Yes):
    with mock.patch.object(app.app.mount.model, 'clearAlign', return_value=
        False):
        with qtbot.waitSignal(app.app.message) as blocker:
            suc = app.clearModel()
            assert not suc
            assert ['Actual model cannot be cleared', 2] == blocker.args
